            <h2>Refund Policy</h2>

            <p>Saudi Arabian Airlines is authorized as a 4-Star Airline for its service at the airport and onboard. The traveler must fill out a refund demand form for a refund. Saudi Arabian Airlines has implemented a 24-hour <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/saudi-arabian-airlines-cancellation-policy.aspx">cancellation policy</a> in response to passenger requirements and circumstances. Saudi Arabian Airlines offers the convenience of canceling a flight online. Only qualifying Saudi Arabian Airlines <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/">flight tickets</a> that are canceled within the active period are eligible for a refund. If flights are canceled due to unavoidable circumstances on the airline's part, travelers are offered reimbursement to book the next ticket. For both local and international flights, Saudi Arabian Airlines has imposed a cancellation fee. </p>

            <h3>FAQs</h3>

            <h3>How to cancel a flight ticket with Saudi Arabian airlines? </h3>
            <p>If you have a flight reservation with Saudi Arabian Airlines but need to cancel it due to any reason. You can cancel it online or get it canceled by Telephone. Call on the customer care phone number to cancel your Saudi Arabian airline ticket. To begin the cancellation process, have your flight confirmation number ready to enter or present to the aviation executive. You will be informed of the refund alternatives available once the Saudi Arabian Airlines cancellation process is completed. </p>
            <h3>When can I request the refund? When can I expect it? </h3>
            <p>After the withdrawal request is accepted, the repayment will be done within 7-10 business days. After reducing the cancellation charges if applicable, the rest amount will be credited to the same payment method which was used at the time of the booking. </p>
            <h3>Can I ask for compensation if my flight gets delayed by 2 hours? </h3>
            <p>A canceled flight can entirely frustrate your journey and delay your travel plans. If the delay was caused by Saudi Arabian Airlines, you are legally entitled to compensation if the alternate flight is delayed by two or more hours. </p>
            <h3>How to check if my flight is refundable? </h3>
            <p>Visit Saudi Arabian Airlines' website to check if the flight ticket is refundable or not. Enter the ticket or flight confirmation number then instantly the refund eligibility and information will be displayed. In case the ticket is not refundable, a passenger can cancel his or her journey and apply the price to book a Saudi Arabian Airlines flight in the future. </p>
            <h3>What is the best way to see if my airline is refundable? </h3>
            <p>Check the reimbursement section of the chosen airline service's terms and conditions to see if a full refund or a partial refund is available. When your preferred airlines allow partial refunds, users can browse for fully refundable plane tickets. </p>
            <h3>Does Saudi Arabian Airlines have access to Wi-Fi? </h3>
